        <title type="html"><![CDATA[Swipload 3.4.0 release notes]]></title>
        <id>https://docs.swipload.com/release-notes/3.4.0</id>
        <link href="https://docs.swipload.com/release-notes/3.4.0"/>
        <updated>2023-12-13T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[This release add new features for shippers and carriers and fixes several issues in the UI .]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="shipments">Shipments<a href="https://docs.swipload.com/release-notes/3.4.0#shipments" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Shipments" title="Direct link to Shipments">​</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="features">Features<a href="https://docs.swipload.com/release-notes/3.4.0#features" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Features" title="Direct link to Features">​</a></h3>
<h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="shippers-can-now-set-base-price--expenses-as-a-default-price-format-for-a-carrier-3007">Shippers can now set "Base price + expenses" as a default price format for a Carrier #3007<a href="https://docs.swipload.com/release-notes/3.4.0#shippers-can-now-set-base-price--expenses-as-a-default-price-format-for-a-carrier-3007" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Shippers can now set &quot;Base price + expenses&quot; as a default price format for a Carrier #3007" title="Direct link to Shippers can now set &quot;Base price + expenses&quot; as a default price format for a Carrier #3007">​</a></h4>
<h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="agreements-will-now-also-affect-shipment">Agreements will now also affect Shipment<a href="https://docs.swipload.com/release-notes/3.4.0#agreements-will-now-also-affect-shipment" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Agreements will now also affect Shipment" title="Direct link to Agreements will now also affect Shipment">​</a></h4>
<p>Most importantly, Shippers will now be able to edit Freights that are a part of Shipments according to the existing agreement rule that allows changes to be made until given status. #3033</p>
<h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="carriers-now-see-new-price-type-base-price--expenses-when-filtering-their-shipment-lists-2990">Carriers now see new price type "Base price + expenses" when filtering their Shipment lists #2990<a href="https://docs.swipload.com/release-notes/3.4.0#carriers-now-see-new-price-type-base-price--expenses-when-filtering-their-shipment-lists-2990" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Carriers now see new price type &quot;Base price + expenses&quot; when filtering their Shipment lists #2990" title="Direct link to Carriers now see new price type &quot;Base price + expenses&quot; when filtering their Shipment lists #2990">​</a></h4>
<h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="will-be-easier-for-shipper-to-compare-prices-of-different-freights">Will be easier for Shipper to compare prices of different freights<a href="https://docs.swipload.com/release-notes/3.4.0#will-be-easier-for-shipper-to-compare-prices-of-different-freights" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Will be easier for Shipper to compare prices of different freights" title="Direct link to Will be easier for Shipper to compare prices of different freights">​</a></h4>
<p>We now display price / kg on the Shipment page. #2962</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="changes">Changes<a href="https://docs.swipload.com/release-notes/3.4.0#changes" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Changes" title="Direct link to Changes">​</a></h3>
<h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="phone-number-prefix-no-longer-based-on-ip-address">Phone number prefix no longer based on IP-address<a href="https://docs.swipload.com/release-notes/3.4.0#phone-number-prefix-no-longer-based-on-ip-address" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Phone number prefix no longer based on IP-address" title="Direct link to Phone number prefix no longer based on IP-address">​</a></h4>
<p>No longer show a user an incorrect flag icon / prefix when inputting phone numbers, as these were based on VPN / ISPs IP-address #2942</p>
<h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="more-information-when-a-price-is-changed">More information when a price is changed<a href="https://docs.swipload.com/release-notes/3.4.0#more-information-when-a-price-is-changed" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to More information when a price is changed" title="Direct link to More information when a price is changed">​</a></h4>
<p>Shipment log will now show what price was changed from and to. #2953</p>
<h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="easier-to-see-which-freight-orders-have-deviations-from-the-pod-list-2973">Easier to see which Freight orders have deviations from the POD-list #2973<a href="https://docs.swipload.com/release-notes/3.4.0#easier-to-see-which-freight-orders-have-deviations-from-the-pod-list-2973" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Easier to see which Freight orders have deviations from the POD-list #2973" title="Direct link to Easier to see which Freight orders have deviations from the POD-list #2973">​</a></h4>
<h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="shippers-now-prompted-if-they-really-want-to-send-a-shipment-with-the-default-price-format-3004">Shippers now prompted if they really want to send a Shipment with the default price format #3004<a href="https://docs.swipload.com/release-notes/3.4.0#shippers-now-prompted-if-they-really-want-to-send-a-shipment-with-the-default-price-format-3004" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Shippers now prompted if they really want to send a Shipment with the default price format #3004" title="Direct link to Shippers now prompted if they really want to send a Shipment with the default price format #3004">​</a></h4>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="fixes">Fixes<a href="https://docs.swipload.com/release-notes/3.4.0#fixes" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Fixes" title="Direct link to Fixes">​</a></h3>
<ul>
<li>Shippers can clearly see where/how to edit the price of a shipment. #2930</li>
<li>User can no longer open multiple context menus #2858</li>
<li>Deviation icon no longer covers up other icons on freight ribbons #2931</li>
<li>Anonymous users will now see status of freights updated upon signing #3012</li>
<li>Stop showing zeroes ("0") when shipper hasn't input a value for freight dimensions (for example weight or LDM) #3017</li>
<li>No longer presented with the option to remove a freight from its original shipment #3019</li>
<li>Freight shippers now get same context menu options as Shipment shippers #2875</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="rss-feed">RSS Feed<a href="https://docs.swipload.com/release-notes/3.4.0#rss-feed" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to RSS Feed" title="Direct link to RSS Feed">​</a></h2>
<p>Subscribe to all our release notes via RSS. The feeds can be found at:</p>
<div class="tabs-container tabList__CuJ"><ul role="tablist" aria-orientation="horizontal" class="tabs"><li role="tab" tabindex="0" aria-selected="true" class="tabs__item tabItem_LNqP tabs__item--active">RSS</li><li role="tab" tabindex="-1" aria-selected="false" class="tabs__item tabItem_LNqP">Atom</li><li role="tab" tabindex="-1" aria-selected="false" class="tabs__item tabItem_LNqP">JSON</li></ul><div class="margin-top--md"><div role="tabpanel" class="tabItem_Ymn6"><div class="language-text codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-text codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">https://docs.swipload.com/release-notes/rss.xml</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><div role="tabpanel" class="tabItem_Ymn6" hidden=""><div class="language-text codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-text codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">https://docs.swipload.com/release-notes/atom.xml</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGrou